dataIdInfo.idPurp: The Multidimension Supplemental toolbox, version 1.1, is a collection of tools which extend the functionality of the core tools of the Multidimension toolbox. These tools can be used as-is or you can modify them to handle specific use cases.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: The Multidimension Supplemental Tools, v 1.2, contains supplemental tools that extend the functionality of the core tools of the ArcGIS Multidimension toolbox. The minimum requirement for this toolbox is ArcGIS 10.1 SP1. The zonal tools require the Spatial Analyst extension.
